      <p>Short for Johannes, a name for the Portuguese gold coin Dobra de 4 escudos, worth in sterling 1.80 (John J. McCusker, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Money and Exchange in Europe and America, 16001775: A Handbook</span>, Chapel Hill, 1978, p. 12).</p>
     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA05d210n2-ptr" id="PJA05d210n2">2</a>
